query:
SELECT id AS "id!: Uuid",
                      workspace_id AS "workspace_id!: Uuid",
                      executor AS "executor!",
                      created_at AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                      updated_at AS "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
               FROM sessions
               WHERE workspace_id = $1
               ORDER BY created_at DESC
